metadata.name: GreenEarthDAO #1
metadata.description:
GreenEarthDAO NFT is an NFT issued in Ethereum blockchain.
With it, you can use APP+cloud storage to take photos of animals and plants and record the time, geographical location and photo digital ID on the blockchain. This unique time, geographic and temperature data would be stored on the blockchain for further scientific research to discover new species.
With it, you can take photos of animals and plants in a Photo-to-Earn business model, to build the first virtual reality combination meta universe project to protecting the earth.
